I"6<p class="intro"><span class="dropcap">T</span>he value of a good mentor is immeasurable. In addition to being someone you can look up to, a mentor can provide you with practical advice on how to get into your field of interest, and with an example of what working in that field might be like day-to-day. They can also help you discover other potential career paths based on your interests, and expand your network by connecting you with their colleagues. And when you encounter obstacles, a mentor can give encouragement and validation to help you through it.
